WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.702
Having a day off?
[Episode 2: Most Familiar Stranger]

00:00:02.702 --> 00:00:04.104
That's a refreshing excuse.

00:00:04.104 --> 00:00:06.473
Just admit you were skipping classes.

00:00:06.473 --> 00:00:08.208
You're starting your one-month
volunteer service this week.

00:00:08.208 --> 00:00:09.209
Sir.

00:00:09.209 --> 00:00:10.643
Head of student affairs is asking for you.

00:00:10.643 --> 00:00:12.345
All right.

00:00:12.345 --> 00:00:13.380
Stop staring.

00:00:13.380 --> 00:00:15.084
Wait here until I'm back.

00:00:21.321 --> 00:00:22.889
He's gone.

00:00:22.889 --> 00:00:24.560
Stop squatting.

00:00:25.792 --> 00:00:27.193
Sorry about that.

00:00:27.193 --> 00:00:28.595
I thought you wanted to skip classes, too.

00:00:28.595 --> 00:00:30.530
So, I dragged you along.

00:00:30.530 --> 00:00:32.486
The mistake's been made.

00:00:34.934 --> 00:00:37.804
1, 4, 2, 8, 5, 7.

00:00:38.471 --> 00:00:41.174
- 1, 4, 2...
- What are you reciting?

00:00:41.174 --> 00:00:43.292
None of your business.

00:00:44.744 --> 00:00:47.380
Hello, I'm Chen Hao Wei from Class 2.

00:00:47.380 --> 00:00:49.015
I didn't ask for an introduction.

00:00:49.015 --> 00:00:51.878
And please stop grinning..

00:00:54.421 --> 00:00:55.964
Fine.

00:00:58.458 --> 00:01:00.427
Hey, you don't have to hang it that low.

00:01:00.427 --> 00:01:03.090
You can shift it up a little.

00:01:03.930 --> 00:01:05.532
To your shoulders.

00:01:05.532 --> 00:01:07.016
I'll help you.

00:01:13.473 --> 00:01:15.146
Isn't this much better?

00:01:53.518 --> 00:01:57.899
[Adapted from Zhong Min Rui's novel]

00:01:58.886 --> 00:01:59.886
So damn heavy.

00:01:59.886 --> 00:02:01.321
Hey, come and help me.

00:02:01.321 --> 00:02:02.555
Chen Hao Wei!

00:02:02.555 --> 00:02:04.051
Coming!

00:02:14.567 --> 00:02:16.528
Excuse me, coming through!

00:02:17.403 --> 00:02:19.015
Coming!

00:02:22.308 --> 00:02:24.051
- Move it in.
- Chen Hao Wei.

00:02:26.646 --> 00:02:30.053
Dad, he's the new hire?

00:02:34.754 --> 00:02:38.558
Young man, who are you calling your dad?

00:02:38.558 --> 00:02:39.859
Is he your friend?

00:02:39.859 --> 00:02:41.294
I thought he was a guest.

00:02:41.294 --> 00:02:43.305
Why act like you don't know me?

00:02:43.930 --> 00:02:45.865
But I don't know you.

00:02:45.865 --> 00:02:48.101
Did you stay here yesterday?

00:02:48.101 --> 00:02:49.996
Where else would I be?

00:02:50.937 --> 00:02:54.175
Hao Wei, go check if there are check-ins.

00:02:58.378 --> 00:02:59.746
Isn't this enough?

00:02:59.746 --> 00:03:02.048
Is it that fun pranking your own son?

00:03:02.048 --> 00:03:03.116
This is ridiculous.

00:03:03.116 --> 00:03:05.610
No way I'll fail to recognize my kid.

00:03:07.787 --> 00:03:09.222
Fine, true.

00:03:09.222 --> 00:03:10.723
You detest me anyway.

00:03:10.723 --> 00:03:12.292
I'm a disgrace.

00:03:12.292 --> 00:03:14.060
So, you want to cut ties with me?

00:03:14.060 --> 00:03:15.461
Fine.

00:03:15.461 --> 00:03:18.264
There aren't any other new guest records.

00:03:18.264 --> 00:03:19.299
Heard that?

00:03:19.299 --> 00:03:20.299
You didn't register.

00:03:20.299 --> 00:03:21.834
You don't stay here, and you aren't a guest.

00:03:21.834 --> 00:03:23.069
Are you a thief?

00:03:23.069 --> 00:03:25.271
You guys are so childish.

00:03:25.271 --> 00:03:27.106
Is there anything worth stealing here?

00:03:27.106 --> 00:03:28.141
Why are you so rude?

00:03:28.141 --> 00:03:29.342
What do you mean by that?

00:03:29.342 --> 00:03:30.577
You don't stay here, and I don't know you.

00:03:30.577 --> 00:03:31.544
Please leave.

00:03:31.544 --> 00:03:32.679
- You're trespassing.
- Where else can I go?

00:03:32.679 --> 00:03:34.013
- Why should I leave?
- I don't even know you.

00:03:34.013 --> 00:03:35.648
- Please leave. This is private property.
- What the heck?

00:03:35.648 --> 00:03:37.884
- I haven't eaten yet. Let go of me.
- Leave before I call the police.

00:03:37.884 --> 00:03:39.886
- Leave.
- Stop shoving me.

00:03:39.886 --> 00:03:40.920
Fine, I'll stop.

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:44.012
I'll leave, all right?

00:03:53.766 --> 00:03:56.936
Hao Wei, I'll check if anything's missing.

00:03:56.936 --> 00:03:58.404
Move everything out of the car.

00:03:58.404 --> 00:03:59.603
Okay.

00:04:23.630 --> 00:04:24.664
Li Wan Zhe.

00:04:24.664 --> 00:04:25.965
A full bowl.

00:04:27.433 --> 00:04:29.168
What's up? Waging another war with your dad?

00:04:29.168 --> 00:04:31.004
He went bonkers this morning.

00:04:31.004 --> 00:04:32.205
Pretended he didn't know me.

00:04:32.205 --> 00:04:34.440
He even called me a thief
and threatened to call the police.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:36.009
So freaking childish.

00:04:36.009 --> 00:04:37.477
All that nonsense about not knowing me.

00:04:37.477 --> 00:04:39.345
He doesn't know me?

00:04:39.345 --> 00:04:41.541
Who else can I be?

00:04:45.918 --> 00:04:47.245
What's wrong?

00:04:51.457 --> 00:04:52.920
What are you doing?

00:04:54.427 --> 00:04:55.995
Li Wan Zhe.

00:04:55.995 --> 00:04:57.563
Say my name.

00:04:57.563 --> 00:04:59.202
He Xiang Yong.

00:05:02.368 --> 00:05:04.604
Why can't I say my name?

00:05:04.604 --> 00:05:06.406
He Xiang Yong, He Xiang Yong, He Xiang Yong.

00:05:06.406 --> 00:05:08.074
- Stop pretending.
- I'm serious.

00:05:08.074 --> 00:05:09.876
- I can't say my name.
- How's that possible?

00:05:09.876 --> 00:05:12.078
He Xiang Yong, He Xiang Yong, He Xiang Yong.

00:05:12.078 --> 00:05:13.079
I can't say it.

00:05:13.079 --> 00:05:15.281
Mom, say his name.

00:05:15.281 --> 00:05:16.582
How the heck would I know that?

00:05:16.582 --> 00:05:18.184
Isn't he a new friend of yours?

00:05:18.184 --> 00:05:20.053
- You don't recognize him?
- Who is he?

00:05:20.053 --> 00:05:21.921
- None of you know him?
- Yeah, we don't.

00:05:21.921 --> 00:05:23.056
Even the village chief doesn't know who he is.

00:05:23.056 --> 00:05:25.024
- Why would we know him?
- He's He Xiang Yong.

00:05:25.024 --> 00:05:26.459
He Xiang Yong doesn't look like this.

00:05:26.459 --> 00:05:28.161
Stop fooling around.

00:05:28.161 --> 00:05:29.562
He is He Xiang Yong.

00:05:29.562 --> 00:05:30.697
Is it April Fool's Day?

00:05:30.697 --> 00:05:32.432
Yeah, it isn't even April Fool's.

00:05:32.432 --> 00:05:34.300
Do I look any different?

00:05:34.300 --> 00:05:35.401
No, you look just like you.

00:05:35.401 --> 00:05:38.107
- Nothing's changed.
- Shit, this is strange.

00:05:38.805 --> 00:05:41.507
I know, give me your phone.

00:05:41.507 --> 00:05:44.505
No one recognizes me, but I can send a message.

00:05:45.144 --> 00:05:46.446
Why aren't you connected to the internet?

00:05:46.446 --> 00:05:48.614
Impossible, I paid the fees yesterday.

00:05:48.614 --> 00:05:49.978
It's connected.
[Li Wan Zhe]

00:05:52.585 --> 00:05:53.619
But there's no service.

00:05:53.619 --> 00:05:54.821
Did you do anything special yesterday?

00:05:54.821 --> 00:05:56.190
Or eat anything strange?

00:05:56.190 --> 00:05:57.223
Yesterday...

00:05:57.223 --> 00:05:58.991
- Weren't we at the dinner gathering?
- Yeah.

00:05:58.991 --> 00:06:00.326
After that, we went to the seaside.

00:06:00.326 --> 00:06:02.134
And then I went home.

00:06:02.795 --> 00:06:04.330
Mr. Hua made me garlic prawn flat noodles.

00:06:04.330 --> 00:06:05.628
And that's all.

00:06:07.367 --> 00:06:08.935
Got it, it must be Mr. Hua.

00:06:08.935 --> 00:06:11.838
He drugged your noodles and changed you.

00:06:11.838 --> 00:06:14.207
Li Wan Zhe, don't be ridiculous.

00:06:14.207 --> 00:06:15.942
- I have no time for your nonsense.
- I'm serious.

00:06:15.942 --> 00:06:19.583
The seaside is most dangerous at night.

00:06:23.082 --> 00:06:26.018
Hong, who are you trying to scare
by acting like a ghost?

00:06:26.018 --> 00:06:29.021
A ghost wouldn't scare anyone.

00:06:29.021 --> 00:06:31.691
Only other stuff are scary.

00:06:31.691 --> 00:06:33.419
What does that mean?

00:06:37.196 --> 00:06:39.031
Did you two go to the seaside last night?

00:06:39.031 --> 00:06:40.546
Yeah.

00:06:48.841 --> 00:06:50.486
That's so dangerous.

00:06:51.144 --> 00:06:53.559
Strange things are bound to happen.

00:06:55.014 --> 00:06:57.597
Hong, do you recognize him?

00:07:09.128 --> 00:07:11.230
Shooting stars are the most beautiful.

00:07:11.230 --> 00:07:12.632
I love shooting stars.

00:07:12.632 --> 00:07:16.261
But there aren't any shooting stars in the day,

00:07:18.037 --> 00:07:20.012
No, I meant...

00:07:20.873 --> 00:07:25.511
Shooting stars... That's it.

00:07:25.511 --> 00:07:26.712
What?

00:07:26.712 --> 00:07:28.147
Didn't you make a wish?

00:07:28.147 --> 00:07:31.417
You wished that no one would recognize you
after you woke up, right?

00:07:31.417 --> 00:07:32.685
You didn't want to be He Xiang Yong anymore.

00:07:32.685 --> 00:07:35.254
I really hope I can stop being He Xiang Yong.

00:07:35.254 --> 00:07:36.589
Dive in!

00:07:36.589 --> 00:07:38.291
I'll jump down and restart my life.

00:07:38.291 --> 00:07:39.954
I was just kidding!

00:07:41.761 --> 00:07:42.762
How's that possible?

00:07:42.762 --> 00:07:44.330
I wasn't being serious with the wish.

00:07:44.330 --> 00:07:47.400
Besides, you also said we've made
so many wishes since we were kids.

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:48.701
Which one of those wishes ever came true?

00:07:48.701 --> 00:07:50.676
Well, do you have a better explanation?

00:07:54.607 --> 00:07:57.610
Fine, let's assume you're right.

00:07:57.610 --> 00:07:59.512
Why did my wish come true, but not yours?

00:07:59.512 --> 00:08:00.680
Didn't you make a wish, too?

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:03.115
Look, the old must make way for the new.

00:08:03.115 --> 00:08:05.585
It's the same with bags and jobs.

00:08:05.585 --> 00:08:07.553
Don't be so harsh on yourself.

00:08:07.553 --> 00:08:10.523
You're already much more
outstanding than I am, you know.

00:08:10.523 --> 00:08:12.625
Sometimes, I really envy you.

00:08:12.625 --> 00:08:14.560
What's there to envy?

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:16.529
You can get up any time you want every morning.

00:08:16.529 --> 00:08:18.297
And you can start work
whenever you feel like it.

00:08:18.297 --> 00:08:20.466
You don't have to face
toxic relationships either.

00:08:20.466 --> 00:08:22.535
And your shaved ice shop is just
a five-minutes walk from your house.

00:08:22.535 --> 00:08:25.538
But life's so much less thrilling.

00:08:25.538 --> 00:08:27.073
I did invite you to jump into the sea with me.

00:08:27.073 --> 00:08:28.541
I'm not looking for that kind of thrill.

00:08:28.541 --> 00:08:30.015
What else do you want?

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:32.311
Well...

00:08:32.311 --> 00:08:33.646
I want to fall in love.

00:08:33.646 --> 00:08:35.021
What?

00:08:36.215 --> 00:08:37.850
I want to be in love.

00:08:37.850 --> 00:08:40.119
Well, go date someone.

00:08:40.119 --> 00:08:43.007
But I want a passionate relationship.

00:08:44.724 --> 00:08:45.756
I don't get it.

00:08:45.756 --> 00:08:46.993
Are you an idiot?

00:08:46.993 --> 00:08:48.027
I mean...

00:08:48.027 --> 00:08:51.430
I want happiness
that's fleeting yet lasts forever.

00:08:51.430 --> 00:08:52.632
Just like fireworks.

00:08:52.632 --> 00:08:53.699
Pew...

00:08:53.699 --> 00:08:55.038
Boom!

00:08:57.103 --> 00:08:59.138
Maybe... the shooting stars just love you.

00:08:59.138 --> 00:09:01.145
So, I'm not affected.

00:09:04.076 --> 00:09:05.144
This is ridiculous.

00:09:05.144 --> 00:09:06.345
Trust me.

00:09:06.345 --> 00:09:09.682
In this world, there are countless
inexplicable things.

00:09:09.682 --> 00:09:12.585
You'll just have to accept it when it hits you.

00:09:12.585 --> 00:09:13.853
So, just accept how things are.

00:09:13.853 --> 00:09:15.154
Wait...

00:09:15.154 --> 00:09:18.925
Well, didn't you hate
living He Xiang Yong's life?

00:09:18.925 --> 00:09:20.059
Take this chance

00:09:20.059 --> 00:09:21.727
and live an entirely new life.

00:09:21.727 --> 00:09:24.063
You're free now.

00:09:24.063 --> 00:09:27.139
You're no longer that He Xiang Yong
who disappointed everyone.

00:09:28.534 --> 00:09:30.670
Are you being serious?

00:09:30.670 --> 00:09:33.520
How about you try saying "He Xiang Yong"?

00:09:36.609 --> 00:09:38.980
Look. It's the heaven's will.

00:09:42.548 --> 00:09:43.950
Fine.

00:09:43.950 --> 00:09:45.017
What now?

00:09:45.017 --> 00:09:46.118
Where do I sleep tonight?

00:09:46.118 --> 00:09:47.219
Go on home.

00:09:47.219 --> 00:09:48.220
Home?

00:09:48.220 --> 00:09:50.590
Didn't you hear me?
My dad wants to call the police on me.

00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:52.725
Just leave it to me.

00:09:52.725 --> 00:09:53.859
See you back at your home in two hours.

00:09:53.859 --> 00:09:56.028
I'll handle this.

00:09:56.028 --> 00:09:58.564
Li Wan Zhe. Hey...

00:09:58.564 --> 00:09:59.565
I'll be waiting for you.

00:09:59.565 --> 00:10:01.088
Li Wan Zhe.

00:10:06.072 --> 00:10:08.197
This is ridiculous.

00:10:17.817 --> 00:10:19.265
Hao Wei.

00:10:20.853 --> 00:10:22.571
Get down here.

00:10:31.664 --> 00:10:33.099
What's up?

00:10:35.101 --> 00:10:38.056
Get that young man from this morning here.

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:41.552
Why the sudden decision?

00:10:43.509 --> 00:10:46.531
He looks suspicious.

00:10:46.531 --> 00:10:48.652
But he's also seems so pitiful.

00:10:51.450 --> 00:10:52.939
Are you sure?

00:11:01.227 --> 00:11:03.484
I think he needs some help, too.

00:11:04.163 --> 00:11:06.060
Get him here.

00:11:08.167 --> 00:11:09.735
But I'm not done drying the winter jackets.

00:11:09.735 --> 00:11:11.644
I'll do it, so get him here.

00:11:31.824 --> 00:11:33.192
Even you're going against me.

00:11:33.192 --> 00:11:35.041
Can't you cooperate?

00:12:03.389 --> 00:12:05.128
I finally found you.

00:12:08.627 --> 00:12:10.529
Living at our inn doesn't cost much.

00:12:10.529 --> 00:12:12.510
I'll pay you later.

00:12:20.206 --> 00:12:22.456
Have we met somewhere?

00:12:23.242 --> 00:12:26.509
Nope, never.

00:12:30.449 --> 00:12:32.518
But where are you planning on walking to?

00:12:32.518 --> 00:12:34.552
How is that your concern?

00:12:45.865 --> 00:12:47.800
What are you still doing here?

00:12:47.800 --> 00:12:49.631
Stop following me.

00:13:20.065 --> 00:13:21.167
Here, take it.

00:13:21.167 --> 00:13:22.501
There's water and medicine in it.

00:13:22.501 --> 00:13:24.002
Oh, and slippers.

00:13:28.073 --> 00:13:29.942
Treat your wound first.

00:13:29.942 --> 00:13:32.812
You'll get an infection,
and it'll hurt like hell.

00:13:32.812 --> 00:13:34.250
Take it.

00:13:49.361 --> 00:13:51.692
Do you know why the sea is blue?

00:13:54.967 --> 00:13:56.635
That's because it has fish in it.

00:13:56.635 --> 00:13:58.871
They go "blue, blue, blue".

00:13:58.871 --> 00:14:00.445
So dumb.

00:14:08.714 --> 00:14:11.518
Why did you say you were
the boss's son this morning?

00:14:13.786 --> 00:14:15.529
I was talking nonsense.

00:14:16.722 --> 00:14:18.591
That's quite an imagination.

00:14:18.591 --> 00:14:20.499
What about me?

00:14:20.499 --> 00:14:22.567
Why do you know my name?

00:14:23.362 --> 00:14:25.965
Thanks for the medicine, water, and slippers.

00:14:25.965 --> 00:14:28.500
I'll pay you for them,
along with the accommodation fees.

00:14:35.374 --> 00:14:37.577
Did something happen?

00:14:37.577 --> 00:14:38.577
Or are you in some kind of trouble?

00:14:38.577 --> 00:14:40.922
Are you always so curious about strangers?

00:14:43.515 --> 00:14:46.615
But you didn't act
like a stranger this morning.

00:14:55.160 --> 00:14:58.864
Fine, I'll tell you.

00:14:58.864 --> 00:15:01.166
This is just a huge misunderstanding.

00:15:01.166 --> 00:15:02.935
So, don't be too bothered.

00:15:02.935 --> 00:15:04.403
My identity doesn't matter either.

00:15:04.403 --> 00:15:06.472
A stranger means you don't know me.

00:15:06.472 --> 00:15:07.699
Okay?

00:15:08.841 --> 00:15:10.246
Thanks.

00:15:15.582 --> 00:15:16.648
If you're really in a tough spot,

00:15:16.648 --> 00:15:18.580
we won't make things tough for you.

00:15:19.718 --> 00:15:22.421
Listen, the boss may look fierce,

00:15:22.421 --> 00:15:24.562
but he's really easy to talk to.

00:15:27.626 --> 00:15:29.361
What's the time now?

00:15:29.361 --> 00:15:30.579
Huh?

00:15:31.597 --> 00:15:33.832
What's the time now?

00:15:33.832 --> 00:15:35.251
Why do you want to know?

00:15:38.671 --> 00:15:40.844
12:20, what's up?

00:15:46.478 --> 00:15:48.019
The helmet.

00:15:49.248 --> 00:15:50.798
You've thought things through?

00:16:02.628 --> 00:16:04.539
Are you sure we've never met before?

00:16:07.866 --> 00:16:09.284
We're moving out.

00:16:14.173 --> 00:16:15.576
Chen Hao Wei, you sure you can get me there?

00:16:15.576 --> 00:16:16.608
It's all your fault.

00:16:16.608 --> 00:16:18.143
Were you having tea time with the teachers?

00:16:18.143 --> 00:16:20.245
Hey, I'm building good ties.

00:16:20.245 --> 00:16:21.347
Watch out for pedestrians.

00:16:21.347 --> 00:16:23.115
- Look. Eyes on the road.
- Perfect evasion.

00:16:23.115 --> 00:16:26.151
Don't you think the weather's great today?

00:16:26.151 --> 00:16:28.648
- So wonderful, I'll miss the boat.
- I'm already going at full speed.

00:16:29.355 --> 00:16:30.389
Aren't I a great cyclist?

00:16:30.389 --> 00:16:32.124
We almost fell!

00:16:32.124 --> 00:16:34.126
Don't you know I need my hands to draw?

00:16:34.126 --> 00:16:37.042
- Fine.
- Too fast.

00:16:37.963 --> 00:16:39.098
Hey, aren't I a great cyclist?

00:16:39.098 --> 00:16:40.132
Boats don't fly.

00:16:40.132 --> 00:16:41.734
Why go so fast?

00:16:41.734 --> 00:16:43.402
- It's leaving!
- Fine, I'll speed up!

00:16:43.402 --> 00:16:45.031
I'll go faster.

00:16:46.705 --> 00:16:47.873
- Be careful.
- We're almost there!

00:16:47.873 --> 00:16:49.617
No problem.

00:16:50.869 --> 00:16:53.010
Stop here.

00:16:54.413 --> 00:16:55.681
I'm off. The boat's almost here.

00:16:55.681 --> 00:16:57.750
Tell me when you're back.

00:16:57.750 --> 00:16:59.118
I'll come looking for you.

00:16:59.118 --> 00:17:01.587
You don't have to.
Why make a special trip to pick me up?

00:17:01.587 --> 00:17:02.988
I won't come just to pick you up.

00:17:02.988 --> 00:17:04.923
I just want to have shaved ice up ahead.

00:17:04.923 --> 00:17:07.459
So, I can also come get you.

00:17:07.459 --> 00:17:08.527
Up ahead?

00:17:08.527 --> 00:17:10.829
That's a restaurant.

00:17:10.829 --> 00:17:12.498
Who cares? Get on your boat.

00:17:12.498 --> 00:17:13.899
Fine. Watch the road.

00:17:13.899 --> 00:17:16.010
- Okay. Bye.
- Bye.

00:17:22.274 --> 00:17:24.143
Mr. He, I'll repeat myself one more time.

00:17:24.143 --> 00:17:26.345
They're university classmates.

00:17:26.345 --> 00:17:27.846
They lived in the same dormitory.

00:17:27.846 --> 00:17:29.948
Upper bunk, lower bunk.

00:17:29.948 --> 00:17:31.984
We'll hang out whenever I visit.

00:17:31.984 --> 00:17:33.591
That's who he is.

00:17:35.020 --> 00:17:37.223
So, you know him too.

00:17:37.223 --> 00:17:38.223
I know him very well.

00:17:38.223 --> 00:17:40.592
Mr. He, I've brought him back.

00:17:40.592 --> 00:17:44.196
Come on over.

00:17:44.196 --> 00:17:46.131
Mr. He, let me introduce him.

00:17:46.131 --> 00:17:49.235
This is a good friend of me
and Xiang Yong at university.

00:17:49.235 --> 00:17:50.235
He's Xiao You.

00:17:50.235 --> 00:17:51.537
Yesterday was all a misunderstanding.

00:17:51.537 --> 00:17:52.871
He isn't a thief.

00:17:52.871 --> 00:17:54.440
He was in a bad mood yesterday,

00:17:54.440 --> 00:17:55.641
so he went to the seaside
to get some fresh air.

00:17:55.641 --> 00:17:56.842
He forget about the time,

00:17:56.842 --> 00:17:59.040
came back too late at night,
and no one noticed.

00:18:03.615 --> 00:18:05.250
Yeah.

00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:06.985
That's right.

00:18:06.985 --> 00:18:09.122
You came back with Xiang Yong?

00:18:10.022 --> 00:18:11.290
Yep.

00:18:11.290 --> 00:18:12.974
Where's he?

00:18:14.393 --> 00:18:16.413
I'd love to know, too.

00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:20.365
Well, where do you live? What's your job?

00:18:20.365 --> 00:18:23.065
Why haven't I heard about you from Xiang Yong?

00:18:24.103 --> 00:18:26.171
Mr. He, didn't I just tell you?

00:18:26.171 --> 00:18:29.308
Fine, I'll explain again. So, listen up.

00:18:29.308 --> 00:18:31.910
When Xiao You was on his working vacation,

00:18:31.910 --> 00:18:33.112
he was duped of all his money.

00:18:33.112 --> 00:18:35.013
On his way back, his luggage was stolen.

00:18:35.013 --> 00:18:36.515
All his personal documents are gone.

00:18:36.515 --> 00:18:37.650
He's too scared to go home.

00:18:37.650 --> 00:18:39.785
He may look like this, but he's super capable.

00:18:39.785 --> 00:18:42.654
He's worked at an inn on the edge
of a cliff a thousand meters above the sea.

00:18:42.654 --> 00:18:44.606
He's also worked at an igloo hotel.

00:18:44.606 --> 00:18:46.825
It was -30 degrees Celsius there!

00:18:46.825 --> 00:18:48.627
He Xiang Yong thought he was really capable,

00:18:48.627 --> 00:18:51.884
so he decided this guy
would be perfect working here.

00:18:55.934 --> 00:18:57.035
Yeah.

00:18:58.416 --> 00:19:01.954
Li Wan Zhe's absolutely right.

00:19:03.742 --> 00:19:05.177
Since you're his classmate,

00:19:05.177 --> 00:19:07.179
why didn't you say so?

00:19:07.179 --> 00:19:09.414
You even claimed to be my son.

00:19:09.414 --> 00:19:10.716
Yeah.

00:19:10.716 --> 00:19:13.451
- Didn't you tell me...
- I'm sorry.

00:19:13.451 --> 00:19:16.189
I know it's hard to believe,

00:19:16.189 --> 00:19:19.758
but I get too into trance sometimes.

00:19:19.758 --> 00:19:23.595
I get stuck in a freaking strange state.

00:19:23.595 --> 00:19:26.532
And I just woke up in the morning.

00:19:26.532 --> 00:19:28.367
I think I had a nightmare.

00:19:28.367 --> 00:19:29.401
He disappeared, too.

00:19:29.401 --> 00:19:32.437
So, I was panicking.

00:19:32.437 --> 00:19:34.940
That's why I might've pissed you two off.

00:19:34.940 --> 00:19:36.875
I hope you'll forgive me.

00:19:36.875 --> 00:19:38.944
Look, he just came back from abroad.

00:19:38.944 --> 00:19:41.580
He needs some time to readjust.

00:19:41.580 --> 00:19:43.615
So many things happened, too.

00:19:43.615 --> 00:19:45.502
How could he speak up so easily?

00:19:46.285 --> 00:19:48.787
Mr. He, listen.

00:19:48.787 --> 00:19:50.956
H-His dad's hella stubborn.

00:19:50.956 --> 00:19:52.624
So, his entire morning has been in chaos.

00:19:52.624 --> 00:19:54.660
He mistook you for his dad.

00:19:54.660 --> 00:19:57.015
Are you saying I'm a stubborn old man?

00:19:57.663 --> 00:19:59.494
No, not at all.

00:20:02.234 --> 00:20:04.236
He Xiang Yong's so weird.

00:20:04.236 --> 00:20:07.096
He brought his friend back, but went missing.

00:20:08.307 --> 00:20:10.442
But it'll be great to keep Xiao You around.

00:20:10.442 --> 00:20:14.112
Look, just tell Xiao You
whatever you want to tell Xiang Yong.

00:20:14.112 --> 00:20:16.582
Xiao You will keep you updated on Xiang Yong.

00:20:16.582 --> 00:20:19.351
Killing two birds with one stone!

00:20:19.351 --> 00:20:21.943
Why are you blabbering so much today?

00:20:25.157 --> 00:20:27.496
Wan Zhe says you want to work here
in exchange for a roof over your head.

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:29.494
Yep.

00:20:29.494 --> 00:20:32.030
Your son said the inn needs manpower.

00:20:32.030 --> 00:20:33.599
I...

00:20:33.599 --> 00:20:35.434
I think I'll be great help.

00:20:35.434 --> 00:20:37.980
So, I thought I'd give it a shot.

00:20:38.637 --> 00:20:41.707
Hao Wei, get him registered.

00:20:41.707 --> 00:20:42.739
What?

00:20:42.739 --> 00:20:45.043
He can be your roommate.

00:20:45.043 --> 00:20:46.778
Show him around the inn.

00:20:46.778 --> 00:20:49.040
Get him familiar with his tasks.

00:20:53.952 --> 00:20:56.989
I don't know what you guys are up to,

00:20:56.989 --> 00:20:59.895
but get Xiang Yong to come back soon.

00:21:05.831 --> 00:21:07.407
Come with me.

00:21:09.268 --> 00:21:10.434
All the best.

00:21:11.136 --> 00:21:12.411
All the best.

00:21:18.377 --> 00:21:20.045
I'm such a genius.

00:21:20.045 --> 00:21:21.751
Freaking genius.

00:21:35.661 --> 00:21:37.930
This is the cabinet here.

00:21:39.431 --> 00:21:41.528
Fishing tools everywhere again.

00:21:42.134 --> 00:21:44.136
- Come over here.
- He never keeps the newspapers.

00:21:44.136 --> 00:21:47.144
- I'll teach you how to register guests.
- What the heck? Why leave the phone here?

00:21:53.979 --> 00:21:55.881
What are you doing?

00:21:55.881 --> 00:21:57.449
Don't touch the boss's stuff.

00:21:57.449 --> 00:22:00.018
Don't the fishing tools go in the storage room?

00:22:00.018 --> 00:22:02.062
Our beds are upstairs, right?

00:22:06.592 --> 00:22:07.592
Give it to me first.

00:22:07.592 --> 00:22:08.626
Those are the boss's fishing tools.

00:22:08.626 --> 00:22:10.469
He'll get angry if you move them around.

00:22:18.910 --> 00:22:20.565
Hey.

00:22:26.700 --> 00:22:28.980
Bathroom and shower are on the left.

00:22:28.980 --> 00:22:30.515
- And...
- Kitchen's on the right.

00:22:30.515 --> 00:22:32.230
I can tell.

00:22:35.987 --> 00:22:37.823
Guest rooms are in the back.

00:22:37.823 --> 00:22:40.098
- We have four-person and six-person rooms.
- Make way, please.

00:22:43.028 --> 00:22:44.997
Follow me, I'll show them to you.

00:22:52.804 --> 00:22:54.893
This is the balcony.

00:22:55.741 --> 00:22:57.362
It's to dry clothes.

00:22:58.009 --> 00:23:00.409
The light bulbs are blown,
and he doesn't even change them?

00:23:01.146 --> 00:23:04.317
This is my favorite place in the inn.

00:23:24.274 --> 00:23:30.650
[Name: Zhong Xiao You]

00:23:51.363 --> 00:23:53.117
Li Wan Zhe.

00:23:56.568 --> 00:23:57.702
What?

00:23:57.702 --> 00:24:00.071
Well? All good?

00:24:00.071 --> 00:24:01.673
Not at all.

00:24:01.673 --> 00:24:03.341
What's wrong?

00:24:03.341 --> 00:24:04.342
These are my old clothes.

00:24:04.342 --> 00:24:05.950
Make do with them for now.

00:24:07.312 --> 00:24:09.114
What now?

00:24:09.114 --> 00:24:10.315
I asked my mom.

00:24:10.315 --> 00:24:12.017
My grandma's auntie's uncle

00:24:12.017 --> 00:24:13.518
made a wish upon a shooting star once.

00:24:13.518 --> 00:24:15.887
His wish came true, and he became rich.

00:24:15.887 --> 00:24:17.056
Can you ask him...

00:24:17.056 --> 00:24:18.056
Are you an idiot?

00:24:18.056 --> 00:24:19.624
It's been a hundred years.
How am I supposed to ask?

00:24:19.624 --> 00:24:20.966
Am I a medium?

00:24:22.093 --> 00:24:24.213
Well, what am I supposed to do?

00:24:25.530 --> 00:24:26.731
Just hang on.

00:24:26.731 --> 00:24:28.233
I'll think of something for you.

00:24:28.233 --> 00:24:30.101
How long do you need?

00:24:30.101 --> 00:24:32.070
If you have time,
make a wish on the shooting stars.

00:24:32.070 --> 00:24:34.272
Are you sure it was the shooting stars?

00:24:34.272 --> 00:24:35.807
The moon works, too.

00:24:35.807 --> 00:24:37.527
Li Wan Zhe!

00:24:38.543 --> 00:24:40.217
Call me if anything happens!

00:24:41.213 --> 00:24:43.106
I don't have a phone.

00:24:47.285 --> 00:24:48.787
Thanks.

00:24:48.787 --> 00:24:50.222
Come back soon.

00:24:50.222 --> 00:24:51.556
Watch your step.

00:24:51.556 --> 00:24:52.591
- Okay.
- Thanks.

00:24:52.591 --> 00:24:53.725
Bye.

00:24:53.725 --> 00:24:55.526
Bye!

00:24:58.129 --> 00:25:00.013
- Hello.
- Hama-chan!

00:25:01.299 --> 00:25:04.436
Have you eaten?

00:25:04.436 --> 00:25:06.104
I ate.

00:25:06.104 --> 00:25:08.740
Want some shaved ice?

00:25:08.740 --> 00:25:09.774
I'm good.

00:25:09.774 --> 00:25:11.142
- Thanks.
- Okay.

00:25:11.142 --> 00:25:14.292
Sorry, we're closing.

00:25:16.948 --> 00:25:20.033
Ma'am, isn't Li Wan Zhe back yet?

00:25:20.652 --> 00:25:22.476
Wan Zhe?

00:25:24.189 --> 00:25:27.692
Li Wan Zhe went out with a new friend today.

00:25:27.692 --> 00:25:31.162
He came back and went out so many times.

00:25:31.162 --> 00:25:32.998
I have no clue where he is.

00:25:32.998 --> 00:25:35.467
No clue when he'll be back either.

00:25:35.467 --> 00:25:37.469
I'm really sorry.

00:25:37.469 --> 00:25:38.570
It's okay.

00:25:38.570 --> 00:25:40.539
Ma'am, I'll help you pack up.

00:25:40.539 --> 00:25:42.140
Oh, you don't have to. Just leave it to me.

00:25:42.140 --> 00:25:44.675
It's fine.

00:25:45.610 --> 00:25:46.711
Thanks.

00:25:46.711 --> 00:25:48.540
You're welcome.

00:25:53.018 --> 00:25:55.167
Hama-chan can smile?

00:25:56.054 --> 00:25:57.522
Just leave it there.

00:25:57.522 --> 00:25:58.623
I'll wash it.

00:25:58.623 --> 00:25:59.987
Okay.

00:26:02.661 --> 00:26:04.520
Damn Li Wan Zhe.

00:26:05.196 --> 00:26:07.820
Why couldn't he have washed them first?

00:26:26.518 --> 00:26:30.021
One day, the farm owner told his cow,

00:26:30.021 --> 00:26:32.123
"Milk yourself today."

00:26:32.924 --> 00:26:35.535
- The cow said..
- Just speak your mind.

00:26:35.535 --> 00:26:37.463
Don't beat around the bush with a joke.

00:26:41.533 --> 00:26:43.702
Is this really your first time here?

00:26:43.702 --> 00:26:46.075
You seem very familiar with this place.

00:26:49.474 --> 00:26:51.509
It's my first time, of course.

00:26:51.509 --> 00:26:55.380
I know my way around
because it's my friend's home.

00:26:55.380 --> 00:26:56.715
I've heard him talk about it.

00:26:56.715 --> 00:26:58.275
So, I know it well.

00:27:01.853 --> 00:27:06.541
But you don't seem like his schoolmate.

00:27:07.258 --> 00:27:09.027
When Mr. He was talking to you,

00:27:09.027 --> 00:27:10.028
you looked really nervous.

00:27:10.028 --> 00:27:12.041
Are you doubting me?

00:27:17.669 --> 00:27:18.770
Sorry about that.

00:27:18.770 --> 00:27:20.577
I am doubting you.

00:27:24.743 --> 00:27:26.211
Fine.

00:27:26.211 --> 00:27:30.282
In that case, can I doubt you as well?

00:27:31.483 --> 00:27:33.195
Where's there to doubt about me?

00:27:35.587 --> 00:27:39.241
Does the boss know
you're his son's high school classmate?

00:27:44.629 --> 00:27:46.417
Don't be surprised.

00:27:47.098 --> 00:27:48.833
I'm on such great terms with him.

00:27:48.833 --> 00:27:53.071
I know everything about him
and his acquaintances.

00:27:53.071 --> 00:27:55.546
How else would I know your name?

00:27:58.443 --> 00:28:00.490
Well, has he ever mentioned me to you?

00:28:01.346 --> 00:28:02.708
Of course.

00:28:04.883 --> 00:28:06.605
What did he tell you?

00:28:09.254 --> 00:28:10.718
You want to know?

00:28:11.856 --> 00:28:13.640
Tell me about it.

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:27.093
He said you're the last person
he wants to remember.

00:28:40.719 --> 00:28:42.437
The better be true.

00:28:45.290 --> 00:28:47.043
Well, take it however you want to.

00:29:00.519 --> 00:29:03.278
[Mr. Chen:
When are you returning to work?]

00:29:03.278 --> 00:29:06.447
[What about all the undone tasks?
Going missing after losing Mr. Lin's funds?]

00:29:35.240 --> 00:29:37.208
How was business today?

00:29:37.208 --> 00:29:38.900
Not bad.

00:29:39.944 --> 00:29:41.913
Tons of customers?

00:29:41.913 --> 00:29:45.116
Same old. A bunch of tourists.

00:29:45.116 --> 00:29:50.221
Your mom said you were out
with a friend the entire day?

00:29:50.221 --> 00:29:51.322
Who is he?

00:29:51.322 --> 00:29:52.976
He Xiang Yong.

00:29:53.591 --> 00:29:55.059
He Xiang Yong?

00:29:56.494 --> 00:29:58.979
Your mom said it was a new friend.

00:30:00.265 --> 00:30:01.266
Let me finish.

00:30:01.266 --> 00:30:04.302
I meant He Xiang Yong's university schoolmate.

00:30:04.302 --> 00:30:05.937
His name is Xiao You.

00:30:05.937 --> 00:30:07.105
Are you good friends with him?

00:30:07.105 --> 00:30:08.407
Great friends, actually.

00:30:08.407 --> 00:30:09.440
How long have you known each other?

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.675
Ages.

00:30:10.675 --> 00:30:12.277
You never said a thing.

00:30:12.277 --> 00:30:15.446
Didn't have many chances to do so.

00:30:15.446 --> 00:30:16.714
You're so strange.

00:30:16.714 --> 00:30:18.945
Why are you bombarding me with questions today?

00:30:21.085 --> 00:30:22.598
B-Because...

00:30:27.841 --> 00:30:30.913
I don't want you hanging out
with people I don't know.

00:30:35.600 --> 00:30:37.335
What are you doing?

00:30:53.084 --> 00:30:54.896
Give me some room.

00:31:29.888 --> 00:31:31.222
It's so hot.

00:31:31.222 --> 00:31:32.790
I'll turn down the temperature.

00:31:32.790 --> 00:31:33.958
Hot?

00:31:33.958 --> 00:31:35.226
Remove your clothes.

00:31:35.226 --> 00:31:36.852
I don't mind.

00:31:40.466 --> 00:31:41.466
I recall now.

00:31:41.466 --> 00:31:44.736
Village Chief Wang said there are leftovers
for the Buddha Jumps Over the Wall.

00:31:44.736 --> 00:31:46.004
I'm worried Du Du will eat it.

00:31:46.004 --> 00:31:47.105
I'll get going first! Du Du!

00:31:47.105 --> 00:31:48.435
Come over here!

00:31:49.841 --> 00:31:51.173
Du Du?

00:32:43.695 --> 00:32:45.108
This smell...

00:32:46.597 --> 00:32:48.733
It's my habit.

00:32:48.733 --> 00:32:51.043
A whiff of it helps me relax.

00:32:53.538 --> 00:32:57.375
That's your habit, not mine.

00:32:57.375 --> 00:32:58.643
Trying to relax?

00:32:58.643 --> 00:33:00.678
The sea breeze is good enough.

00:33:00.678 --> 00:33:03.181
Why use those weird fragrances?

00:33:03.181 --> 00:33:05.046
Weirdo.

00:33:07.552 --> 00:33:09.287
I'm reading.

00:33:09.287 --> 00:33:11.216
I want to sleep.

00:33:21.199 --> 00:33:23.996
Did He Xiang Yong tell you anything else?

00:33:25.103 --> 00:33:27.222
What do you want him to say about you?

00:33:30.775 --> 00:33:32.586
Just making conversation.

00:33:38.416 --> 00:33:40.918
Does he really tell you everything?

00:33:40.918 --> 00:33:45.488
Yep, because I'm his most important friend
who knows him best.

00:33:48.693 --> 00:33:50.361
Doubt so.

00:33:50.361 --> 00:33:52.030
If you were such great friends,

00:33:52.030 --> 00:33:54.685
why did he never talk to Mr. He about you?

00:33:56.467 --> 00:33:58.069
You were from the same high school,

00:33:58.069 --> 00:33:59.337
but you don't ever mention it.

00:33:59.337 --> 00:34:01.524
You're the weirdo here.

00:34:13.818 --> 00:34:15.987
Since we are so doubtful of each other,

00:34:15.987 --> 00:34:17.221
let's just keep a distance.

00:34:17.221 --> 00:34:19.296
It's better to keep out of each other's way.

00:34:19.991 --> 00:34:22.974
Fabulous, exactly what I want.

00:34:57.829 --> 00:34:59.222
All right!

00:35:02.500 --> 00:35:04.302
Think positively.

00:35:04.302 --> 00:35:06.804
It's so rare for a wish to come true.

00:35:06.804 --> 00:35:08.005
If I were you, I'd borrow money.

00:35:08.005 --> 00:35:10.341
I'd renovate, overhaul,
and expand that inn of yours.

00:35:10.341 --> 00:35:12.310
Li Wan Zhe.

00:35:12.310 --> 00:35:14.912
Stop with the irresponsible comments.

00:35:14.912 --> 00:35:17.248
Things aren't so simple.

00:35:17.248 --> 00:35:18.988
It's giving me a splitting headache.

00:35:19.917 --> 00:35:22.470
Now, there's Chen Hao Wei to worry about, too.

00:35:25.723 --> 00:35:27.859
Why are you fine?

00:35:27.859 --> 00:35:28.893
I told you.

00:35:28.893 --> 00:35:30.728
The shooting stars took a liking to you.

00:35:30.728 --> 00:35:32.459
The wish doesn't affect me.

00:35:33.664 --> 00:35:35.500
How's that possible?

00:35:35.500 --> 00:35:37.042
Li Wan Zhe.

00:35:37.902 --> 00:35:39.937
Come on down.

00:35:39.937 --> 00:35:41.439
Why are you so early today?

00:35:41.439 --> 00:35:43.074
Come on up and chat.

00:35:43.074 --> 00:35:44.376
Come down here.

00:35:44.376 --> 00:35:45.376
Nah.

00:35:45.376 --> 00:35:46.711
It's so far, and I'm lazy.

00:35:46.711 --> 00:35:48.479
Hurry up.

00:35:48.479 --> 00:35:50.114
Get up here.

00:35:50.114 --> 00:35:52.258
I like you!

00:35:57.321 --> 00:35:58.486
What?

00:36:00.858 --> 00:36:03.995
My name's Hamaguchi Aomi!

00:36:03.995 --> 00:36:07.098
I was born on January 10, 1998.

00:36:07.098 --> 00:36:09.000
I'm a Scorpio.

00:36:09.000 --> 00:36:10.875
Blood type, AB.

00:36:11.569 --> 00:36:13.504
I love eating plums.

00:36:13.504 --> 00:36:15.506
I hate mushrooms.

00:36:15.506 --> 00:36:16.607
What's with the self-introduction?

00:36:16.607 --> 00:36:18.309
My dream is to travel the world.

00:36:18.309 --> 00:36:21.445
I really want to visit the south pole.

00:36:21.445 --> 00:36:25.216
You're just one person in this world,

00:36:25.216 --> 00:36:28.996
but to a certain person,

00:36:29.987 --> 00:36:32.323
you're their world.

00:36:32.323 --> 00:36:34.091
Li Wan Zhe.

00:36:34.091 --> 00:36:36.240
You are my world.

00:36:37.628 --> 00:36:40.171
I've been in love with you for a long time.

00:36:41.399 --> 00:36:42.900
What?

00:36:42.900 --> 00:36:45.347
Please be my boyfriend.

00:36:55.146 --> 00:36:56.547
I think I've eaten too much watermelon.

00:36:56.547 --> 00:36:57.715
My stomach hurts.

00:36:57.715 --> 00:36:59.504
I need the toilet.

00:37:06.791 --> 00:37:08.726
Wow, what a hilarious joke.

00:37:08.726 --> 00:37:10.962
Hamaguchi Aomi, you're so fluent
in Mandarin now.

00:37:10.962 --> 00:37:12.764
Keep at it. Study hard.

00:37:12.764 --> 00:37:13.797
All the best.

00:37:13.797 --> 00:37:16.100
I'm not joking with you.

00:37:16.100 --> 00:37:18.269
So funny.

00:37:18.269 --> 00:37:19.604
I'm serious.

00:37:19.604 --> 00:37:22.077
I'm serious, too. Such a great joke.

00:37:22.964 --> 00:37:24.675
[Epilogue]

00:37:24.675 --> 00:37:27.111
Thanks.

00:37:27.111 --> 00:37:29.513
I told you not to come pick me up.

00:37:29.513 --> 00:37:31.082
I didn't come here for you.

00:37:31.082 --> 00:37:32.683
I'm here to get shaved ice.

00:37:32.683 --> 00:37:35.152
It takes 20 minutes
to get here from the harbor.

00:37:35.152 --> 00:37:36.354
20 minutes?

00:37:36.354 --> 00:37:38.589
I only took 15 minutes.

00:37:38.589 --> 00:37:40.024
A real cycling god here.

00:37:40.024 --> 00:37:41.919
That'll be my new nickname. Cycling god.

00:37:45.029 --> 00:37:46.395
What's up?

00:37:47.098 --> 00:37:48.666
You used perfume.

00:37:48.666 --> 00:37:49.900
Yep.

00:37:49.900 --> 00:37:51.135
Why the sudden change?

00:37:51.135 --> 00:37:52.169
It's nothing, just...

00:37:52.169 --> 00:37:54.424
I feel at ease with this fragrance around.

00:37:55.373 --> 00:37:56.974
- Want to take a sniff?
- I'm good.

00:37:56.974 --> 00:37:58.175
- Are you sure?
- It's fine.

00:37:58.175 --> 00:38:00.778
I'm more interested in your shaved ice.

00:38:00.778 --> 00:38:02.246
- Shaved ice?
- How about I share some?

00:38:02.246 --> 00:38:03.714
Don't you have your own?

00:38:03.714 --> 00:38:05.850
- Why take mine? I didn't say I wanted it.
- I want to swap with you.

00:38:05.850 --> 00:38:07.618
- Don't mix them.
- I didn't mix them.

00:38:07.618 --> 00:38:08.953
- Taking the green beans again?
- I'll just have a bite.

00:38:08.953 --> 00:38:09.954
I want to try some.

00:38:09.954 --> 00:38:12.256
Let me see if it's better
than my friend's stall.

00:38:12.256 --> 00:38:13.591
Your friend runs a shaved ice stall?

00:38:13.591 --> 00:38:16.661
Yep, the best on the entire island.

00:38:16.661 --> 00:38:18.931
When I visit, I'll have to try it for myself.

00:38:18.931 --> 00:38:19.963
Sure.

00:38:19.963 --> 00:38:23.367
The jelly at his place
is the best I've ever tasted.

00:38:23.367 --> 00:38:28.072
Nah, I think the green bean milk here
is better than your friend's.

00:38:28.072 --> 00:38:29.173
The green bean milk is so good.

00:38:29.173 --> 00:38:30.541
The jelly is the best in the entire world.

00:38:30.541 --> 00:38:32.109
Didn't you want to swap with me?

00:38:32.109 --> 00:38:33.931
I was just curious.

00:38:58.769 --> 00:39:02.106
So, you're the comic artist
working with Xiang Yong?

00:39:02.106 --> 00:39:03.308
Didn't you want to be in love?

00:39:03.308 --> 00:39:04.308
Love has come knocking.

00:39:04.308 --> 00:39:05.643
Why are you so shocked?

00:39:05.643 --> 00:39:06.877
I'm really in love with you.

00:39:06.877 --> 00:39:08.866
No way.

00:39:10.815 --> 00:39:11.849
Silently recite...

00:39:11.849 --> 00:39:14.418
1, 4, 2, 8, 5, 7.

00:39:14.418 --> 00:39:15.886
Why these numbers?

00:39:15.886 --> 00:39:18.243
Did you date He Xiang Yong?